latestIgtvVideos.title: My Acne Scar Journey | How I Clear My Acne Scar With @medermaofficial
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I have been dealing with acne and its scars for more than 10 years. I have been to alot of dermat as well but nothing works. So I gave @medermaindia @medermaofficial a try, It didnt gave me the drastic result but it did clear out alot of my acne scars. I am continuing it for 1 year to see the result because my scars are really old and I know it will take alot of time to heal.  Watch this video to have detailed concept of how this cream works.

Do let me know if you like this❤

latestIgtvVideos.title: Nykaa Haul❤️
💅 Essentials
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
These two nail paints are my favourite from my collection, simply because of its color. I love pastels and I love everything in pastel color. This pastel mint green color and this baby pink color from @facescanada are just love. It looks very beautiful on the nails and makes your looks happy🤗💅
If you buy nail paints dnt forget to buy nail paints remover because anyhow you are applying this which can damage your nails and if you don't take care of your nails, it is gonna be worse. So invest in a good nail paint remover as well. This one is from @lovecolorbar  and I absolutely loved it😍.
